{"tid":1329893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】歐洲議會通過制裁 促歐盟停向香港出口人群管制裝備","createTime":"2019-07-18T10:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T10:53:25.000Z","uid":26418,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab58dc73ad901c4c254a2a901c6b92aa893a3ec","tid":1329893,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2400000/2404537/66425_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2400000%2F2404537%2F66425_600.png&h=5b54ed88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 反修例引發連串風波，歐洲議會通過議案，停向香港出口人群管制裝備。<br />\n<br />\n反修例爭議在海外也持續發酵。歐洲議會通過議案，促歐盟暫停向香港出口或違人權的人群管制裝備。議會議長會將建議轉交歐洲理事會、歐盟成員國28位領袖、歐盟委員會以及中國和香港特區政府。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會本港時間下午4時緊急辯論香港情況，多名議員發言關注修訂逃犯條例及引發的示威。這是1997年香港回歸以來，歐洲議會首次針對香港提出制裁。<br />\n<br />\n議案由多名歐洲議會議員發起，內容表示深切關注香港修訂《逃犯條例》，聲援香港人和平示威反修訂、支持民主及人權，並促請港府對警方過度使用武力的爭議進行獨立調查，以及對4名年輕示威者喪生致深切哀悼。<br />\n<br />\n推動議案歐洲議會議員同時亦強調尊重「一個中國」原則，但促請中方尊重一國兩制，停止「干涉香港內政」。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會除了討論香港外，亦會討論美國墨西哥邊境事宜，以及俄羅斯等有關侵害人權、民主與法治的個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2404537?r=cpstni\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2404537%3Fr%3Dcpstni&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=ca5f245b\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2404537?r=cpstni</a>"},{"pid":"9dee622406109b64bfeb7e5d2790ede193e52eae","tid":1329893,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"提防熱普仇城毛五派搞分化<br />\n721記得五大訴求<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bh1sWtu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbh1sWtu.png&h=eb1b20f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2af81a3024cba4206faf7452abf0a1e2a2c26b2c","tid":1329893,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"肯定準備搵支拿入武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42f37375df79e9a2ce4083c7db5b5bb423136d7","tid":1329893,"uid":26418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"肯定準備搵支那入武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227b139af44c86a58e33a279e43caae3f17ca239","tid":1329893,"uid":64159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2af81a3024cba4206faf7452abf0a1e2a2c26b2c","tid":1329893,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"肯定準備搵支拿入武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"分分鐘係冇煙出嘅催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}